data.description: Welcome Home! This one story, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, concrete block home is ready for you! Spacious backyard has been fully fenced in within the last 2 years. Enjoy your time on the back patio under the sunshade. Escape the Florida heat with your indoor laundry room. Air handler fully refurnished with new interior parts in 2021. Kitchen and dining areas have newer wood-look vinyl flooring. Conveniently located for quick access to SR 520 and I95 as well as Saturn Elementary School and Cocoa High School. Schedule your appointment to see this home today!
